    ("The value of climate modeling for society includes:", ["no practical benefits whatsoever for any decisions today", "informing adaptation planning, mitigation targets, and risk assessment", "only academic publications without any real-world use", "only entertainment and no scientific or policy applications"], 1, "Models are essential tools for climate-informed decision-making."),
