    ("Geological process models simulate events over:", ["only seconds to minutes of observation time", "timescales ranging from seconds (earthquakes) to billions of years (plate tectonics)", "only exactly one million years for all processes uniformly", "only the future and never past geological events at all"], 1, "Different processes require different temporal scales."),
